  "summaries": [
    "<b>Mining armor</b> is an <linked>armor</linked> set consisting of the <b>Mining Helmet</b> or <b><span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Ultrabright Helmet</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span></b>, <b>Mining Shirt</b>, and <b>Mining Pants</b>. The helmets alone provide light when worn in the armor slot, but not when worn in the social slot. A full set grants <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 4 / <span class=\"eico i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 3 defense (6 with the Ultrabright Helmet), as well as 30% increased <linked>mining speed</linked>.",
    "<ul><li>The Mining Shirt and Mining Pants are dropped from <linked>Undead Miners</linked> with a <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"chance\"><s>12*</s>3/25 (12%)</span> / <span class=\"eico i5\" title=\"3DS version\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"chance\"><s>2.4*</s>3/125 (2.4%)</span> chance.</li><li>The Mining Helmet can be purchased from the <linked>Merchant</linked> for <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4 i5\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"coin\" title=\"4 Gold Coins\" data-sort-value=\"40000\"><span class=\"gc\">4</span></span> / <span class=\"eico i3\" title=\"Old-gen console version\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"coin\" title=\"8 Gold Coins\" data-sort-value=\"80000\"><span class=\"gc\">8</span></span>.<ul><li>The Mining Helmet is also a drop from Undead Miners with a <span class=\"chance\"><s>5*</s>1/20 (5%)</span> chance in the <linked>[img:Desktop version]</linked><linked> Desktop version</linked>, <linked>[img:Console version]</linked><linked> Console version</linked>, and <linked>[img:Mobile version]</linked><linked> Mobile version</linked>.</li></ul></li></ul>"
